b1 <- dbGetQuery(con,"SELECT * FROM bridgelog where simulationcode ='2015/12/01littletestwarp1'")
g1 <- dbGetQuery(con,"SELECT * FROM governmentlog where simulationcode ='2015/12/01littletestwarp1'")
